#
# All six datasets are generated by data-raw/generate_example_data.R and
# shipped as compressed .rda files in data/.
#
# Flat-file copies for read_geno() demonstrations live in inst/extdata/:
#   example_genotypes_numeric.csv   (numeric dosage)
#   example_genotypes.hmp.txt       (HapMap)
#   example_genotypes.vcf           (VCF v4.2)
#   example_blues.csv               (pre-adjusted BLUEs: id, YLD, RES)
